Author: Llama#1330
Content: how split up utxo

Author: c2k#4915
Content: in barterdex click exchange on the coin you want to manage your utxo's

Author: c2k#4915
Content: then in the par on the top left click "inventory"

Author: c2k#4915
Content: you should see your utxo's on the lower half of the screen

Author: c2k#4915
Content: if you ahve 1 utxo then you want to select "make inventory" in the center which will split your balance into the lots shown

Author: c2k#4915
Content: im not an expert on utxo's but i think you want your utxo sizes to fairly match the utxo sizes of the other side of the trade

Author: c2k#4915
Content: so if your selling you want your utxo sizes to be similar sizes to the buyers in bdex

Author: c2k#4915
Content: if you send the balance to yourself you will get 1 utxo of your size

Content: then you can re-split
